Comment: see https://github.com/lordmauve/pgzero/issues/75 for discussion of licensing issues
 doc/_static/scratch: screenshots of scratch which I am not clear of licensing of, also flappy bird images seem to have been ripped from commercial flappy bird game
 doc/_static/eep.wav: source and license unknown
 doc/_static/sticker-mule.svg: source and license unknown (strongly suspect nonfree)
 doc/_static/rotation.svg: spaceship was apparently created for the project but who exactly created it and what license they intended to put it under is unknown
 examples/asteroids: license unknown
 examples/basic: license unknown, source of some assets unclear
 examples/flappybird: license unknown, assets seem to have been ripped from the propietary flappy bird game
 examples/mines: license unknown, source of assets unknown
 examples/pong: license unknown
 examples/snake: license unknown, source of assets unknown
 

